{
  "stem": "13213.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 475.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it didn't seem to me that I was that much different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they made us-- when they take you into the ghetto, and de-humanize you, and so on, you really start believing maybe something wrong or something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we didn't give in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were fighting back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, usually bread.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes butter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes in the summer it was some vegetables or fruit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we couldn't bring any meat or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you know, if you have to survive, you're allowed to eat anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father wouldn't eat meat, even though we could get from the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had some, like I said, butter and bread and vegetables and fruit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how we survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was going on until the summer of 1942 until the liquidation started.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few months, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the liquidation, like I said, when I arrived to visit my parents, the liquidation started.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hiding in a attic, in one of rooms, in one of the houses where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Stepan, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was actually near the river name Horyn-- the name of the river, Horyn, in the Stepan, a big river, which goes through there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother and my sister was with me, my mother, and my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we heard the voices, there was crying and screaming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very scary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother told me to jump.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I jumped from the window.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was very high up-- I don't know, like one floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I fell down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then my mother jumped after me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I heard just noise inside the room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Germans-- and the Nazis took my brother, my sister, and my father to the extermination.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
